<br>
Not that I shouldn't do it, but it is a pain. (lol Invis to Animals is still near the front of my spell book...I have only cast that spell once in my game life).  I don't want the day I get the interface to be spent sitting on my butt rearranging spell gems.  Would rather do that over time as I feel like it.<br>
<br>
Yes I still dip into those late pages from time to time.  I buff my pet with Natureskin on those rare ocassions I summon him...that is right at the end of the spellbook.  At some point I will have to sort that.<br>
